This paper deals with information transmission and communication constraints in networks of mobile autonomous agents. The paper discusses the impact of mobility on data transfer and provides bounds on the maximum transmittable data. This topic is closely related to information theory (cs.IT), networked systems (cs.NI), control systems (cs.SY), machine learning (cs.MA), and multimedia (cs.MM).
